transcripts: Then landscape bath accessory collection by Kenneth Cole reaction home was designed exclusively for Bed Bath and Beyond. This collection has a rich stone and wood look, and is made of 100 percent resin making it durable and able to withstand moister. It includes a tooth brush holder, soap dish, lotion pump, waste paper basket, tumbler and boutique tissue holder. All of the Kenneth Cole reaction home bath collections were designed to coordinate with any of the Kenneth Cole reaction home shower curtains. So feel free to mix and match. The landscape bath accessory collection is part of the Kenneth Cole reaction home collection. It is available exclusively online and at select Bed Bath and Beyond stores.
